body_html: I'm not sure if it makes a difference. I did a search and the http version of the link seems to be used 400x more, because it's what the Apache 2.0 license recommends. Although in all fairness, it was written in 2004. It would be a big change to refactor these headers and I'm not sure if it's worth doing.
